params.name: vocab_size
params.description: Vocabulary size of the TrajectoryTransformer model. Defines the number of different tokens that can berepresented by the trajectories passed when calling TrajectoryTransformerModel

params.name: action_weight
params.description: Weight of the action in the loss function

params.name: reward_weight
params.description: Weight of the reward in the loss function

params.name: value_weight
params.description: Weight of the value in the loss function

params.name: block_size
params.description: Size of the blocks in the trajectory transformer.

params.name: action_dim
params.description: Dimension of the action space.

params.name: observation_dim
params.description: Dimension of the observation space.

params.name: transition_dim
params.description: Dimension of the transition space.

params.name: n_layer
params.description: Number of hidden layers in the Transformer encoder.

params.name: n_head
params.description: Number of attention heads for each attention layer in the Transformer encoder.

params.name: n_embd
params.description: Dimensionality of the embeddings and hidden states.

params.name: resid_pdrop
params.description: The dropout probability for all fully connected layers in the embeddings, encoder, and pooler.

params.name: embd_pdrop
params.description: The dropout ratio for the embeddings.

params.name: attn_pdrop
params.description: The dropout ratio for the attention.

params.name: hidden_act
params.description: The non-linear activation function (function or string) in the encoder and pooler. If string, gelu,relu, selu and gelu_new are supported.

params.name: max_position_embeddings
params.description: The maximum sequence length that this model might ever be used with. Typically set this to something largejust in case (e.g., 512 or 1024 or 2048).

params.name: initializer_range
params.description: The standard deviation of the truncated_normal_initializer for initializing all weight matrices.

params.name: layer_norm_eps
params.description: The epsilon used by the layer normalization layers.

params.name: kaiming_initializer_range
params.description: A coefficient scaling the negative slope of the kaiming initializer rectifier for EinLinear layers.

params.name: use_cache
params.description: Whether or not the model should return the last key/values attentions (not used by all models). Onlyrelevant if config.is_decoder=True.
